thread.title: Rose Callaghan
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Rose Callaghan

author: Rose Callaghan
title: Rose Callaghan
text:
Efficient. Professional with a personal touch!
Have been very pleased and comfortable with my dealings with Amanda from Northcote branch of Nelson Alexander. Nothing has been too big nor too small for her to deal with and often thinking outside the usual "square" helps a lot in some situations. Recommend her highly.
